o me"],[5780,5989,"unless you can help me rise to the top."],[6247,6343,"I'll call you when I know"],[6343,6468,"if you're still of use to me."]],"61":[[412,579,"Fuck these assholes!"],[579,742,"Janeen and I will just have to"],[742,938,"figure out another way to handle Dean."],[1259,1355,"Fay, what are you doing?"],[1480,1547,"What does it look like"],[1547,1634,"I'm doing, Daniel?"],[1776,1956,"You know, I thought for a second"],[2014,2181,"that I could navigate this life."],[2248,2339,"But I can't."],[2402,2506,"It's too much."],[2556,2640,"And you know what?"],[2652,2882,"No one should feel like an object,"],[2882,2990,"so I'm leaving."],[3073,3249,"I know that adjusting has been hard."],[3294,3449,"But you're the strongest person"],[3449,3499,"I know."],[3499,3611,"You can do this."],[3611,3724,"You are only saying that"],[3724,3878,"because you want something from me,"],[3878,4054,"just like everyone else!"],[4149,4250,"I do need you."],[4350,4517,"But I care about you, too."],[4763,4946,"I'm sorry for my part in this, Fay."],[4996,5075,"But face it."],[5380,5526,"You were born into this."],[5572,5705,"You're Don Alden's daughter."],[6051,6135,"No matter how much"],[6135,6256,"this world scares you,"],[6331,6435,"it's where you belong."]],"62":[[116,350,"Maybe he’s right..."],[579,642,"Stay."],[746,838,"Make it work."],[992,1067,"In the meantime,"],[1067,1226,"save me from my dad, please."],[1343,1609,"Have you spoken to him since..."],[1609,1822,"Since I got caught in the act again?"],[1897,1956,"No."],[2239,2293,"God."],[2406,2619,"Daniel, you are pretty shit"],[2619,2723,"at keeping this whole"],[2723,2940,"I'm into guys thing a secret."],[3599,3653,"It's Dad."],[3728,3862,"It's time to face the music."],[4275,4408,"It's obvious that you two"],[4408,4646,"have no romantic connection."],[4646,4813,"Dad, let me explain."],[4813,5059,"Daniel, it's not a concern of mine"],[5059,5205,"who you choose to sleep with."],[5259,5526,"I only wish that you trusted me enough"],[5526,5689,"to be honest with me about it."],[5955,6110,"Your engagement is off."],[6160,6281,"I've spread the word"],[6281,6485,"to avoid any further embarrassments."],[6514,6723,"This contract outlines"],[6723,6861,"how we proceed from here."],[7257,7411,"Dad, you can't do this."]],"63":[[83,208,"Dad, you can't do this."],[208,308,"Son, I will do"],[308,467,"whatever I can necessary"],[467,575,"to protect this family."],[713,859,"Hey, you were right to want to leave."],[896,1101,"What he's asking you to do is dangerous."],[1101,1142,"It's..."],[1142,1368,"You'll give me three million dollars"],[1368,1472,"if I date Ivan"],[1472,1639,"and pump him for information?"],[1639,1772,"To pretend to date him."],[1906,2035,"I think you can even convince him"],[2035,2160,"to become an ally of mine."],[2256,2406,"To take down Don Alden."],[2552,2806,"Three million dollars is enough"],[2806,3028,"to help my family and then some..."],[3078,3190,"And at this point,"],[3215,3428,"I'd turn on my father for free."],[3599,3674,"So what do you say?"],[3716,3891,"She's not going to whore herself out"],[3891,3991,"in the line of fire"],[3991,4141,"to help your power grab."],[4183,4287,"She's not a whore."],[4333,4446,"She's an asset."],[4471,4679,"And this power grab benefits all of us."],[4796,4934,"Plus, if she pulls it off,"],[4988,5134,"she'll be a very rich woman."]],"64":[[304,421,"I don't believe this, Fay."],[475,583,"I thought you were tired of"],[583,709,"being used by him."],[709,838,"We're using each other."],[967,1121,"It's like you said, Daniel."],[1234,1388,"I am a part of this family."],[1497,1609,"Might as well lean in"],[1609,1743,"and make the best of it."],[1835,1914,"Good girl."],[2031,2168,"Better yet, smart girl."],[2231,2356,"And where does this leave me?"],[2369,2439,"This leaves you"],[2439,2552,"wherever you want to be."],[2585,2748,"You can go fall in love with Jerome"],[2827,3044,"or someone else who you truly care about."],[3082,3186,"What I want"],